<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "profile.jpg", width: 300, alt: "Profile Image", class: "profile-img" %>
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width:<%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                >
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>
          I have 3+ years of experience as a software engineer building Ruby on Rails applications,
          along with hands on experience in other technologies such as HTML, CSS, JavaScript and SQL.
          I also have good exposure Data Structure and java. 
        </p>
        <p>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ravi-narayan-patel"> See my LinkedIn profile </a>for more career details.
        </p>
        <p>
          <button class="btn btn-primary" 
                  type="button"
                  data-toggle="collapse"
                  data-target="#jobHistory"
                  aria-expanded="false"
                  aria-controller="jobHistory">
            Job History
          </button>
          <button class="btn btn-primary" 
                  type="button"
                  data-toggle="collapse"
                  data-target="#education"
                  aria-expanded="false"
                  aria-controller="education">
            Education
          </button>
        </p>
        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Software Developer at Bonito Designs Bangalore 
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Software Engineer at Carmatec It Sol Pvt Ltd Bangalore 
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Software Engineer at DRG Analytics & Insights Pvt Ltd Bangalore 
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              MCA from University Institute Of Technology, RGPV Bhopal
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              BSc(IT) from Makhanlal chaturvedi rastriya pratrakarita viswavidyalay Bhopal 
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
